            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <figure class="text-center">
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
              <p>Smarting body can attract any guys.Our website is first step to guy. </p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">
              Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Pathin Technology University</cite>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <figure class="text-center">
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
              <p>A regular exercise is also a vital part of any weight loss plan.</p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">
              By Carl Rivera<cite title="Source Title">British</cite>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
 </div>
</main>

<% include ./partial/footer %>
</body>
</html>